'''LZ4'''是一种[[无损数据压缩|无损数据压缩]][[算法|算法]]，着重于压缩和解压缩速度。它属于面向字节的[[LZ77与LZ78|LZ77]]压缩方案家族。

== 特征 ==
该算法提供一个比[[LZO|LZO]]算法稍差的压缩率——这逊于[[gzip|gzip]]等算法。但是，它的压缩速度类似LZO——比gzip快几倍；而解压速度显著快于LZO。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=MTI4NjM|title=Support For Compressing The Linux Kernel With LZ4|accessdate=2015-08-28|author=[[Michael_Larabel|Michael Larabel]]|date=2013-01-28|work=[[Phoronix|Phoronix]]|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127152013/https://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=MTI4NjM}}</ref>

== 设计 ==
压缩可以在流或者块中进行。在查找最佳匹配时投入更多努力可达到更高的压缩率，这样的结果是更小的输出和更快的解压缩速度。

== 实现 ==
Yann Collet使用[[C语言|C语言]]制成的[[参考实现|参考实现]]发布在[[BSD许可证|BSD许可证]]之下。此算法已有多种语言的[[移植_(軟體)|移植]]和[[绑定|绑定]]，包括[[Java|Java]]、[[C♯|C#]]、[[Python|Python]]等。<ref name="homepage">{{GitHub|lz4/lz4|Extremely Fast Compression algorithm http://www.lz4.org}}</ref>像是[[Hadoop|Hadoop]]等数据库使用此算法进行快速压缩。LZ4也在[[Linux内核|Linux内核]] 3.11中被原生实现。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://lwn.net/Articles/557814/|title=Kernel development|accessdate=2015-08-28|author=Jonathan Corbet|date=2013-07-19|publisher=[[LWN.net|LWN.net]]|archive-date=2017-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171215001155/https://lwn.net/Articles/557814/}}</ref>[[ZFS|ZFS]]文件系统的[[FreeBSD|FreeBSD]]、[[Illumos|Illumos]]、ZFS on Linux，以及ZFS-OSX实现都支持LZ4算法进行即时压缩。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.freebsd.org/releases/9.2R/relnotes.html|title=FreeBSD 9.2-RELEASE Release Notes|accessdate=2015-08-28|date=2013-11-13|publisher=[[FreeBSD|FreeBSD]]|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112011553/https://www.freebsd.org/releases/9.2R/relnotes.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://wiki.illumos.org/display/illumos/LZ4+Compression|title=LZ4 Compression|accessdate=2015-08-28|publisher=[[illumos|illumos]]|archive-date=2018-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181009050216/https://wiki.illumos.org/display/illumos/LZ4+Compression}}</ref><ref>{{GitHub|zfsonlinux/zfs/commit/9759c60|Illumos #3035 LZ4 compression support in ZFS and GRUB}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.open-zfs.org/wiki/Features#lz4_compression|title=Features: lz4 compression|accessdate=2015-08-28|publisher=[[OpenZFS|OpenZFS]]|archive-date=2020-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425120324/http://www.open-zfs.org/wiki/Features#lz4_compression}}</ref>Linux从3.19-rc1开始在[[SquashFS|SquashFS]]中支持LZ4。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://git.kernel.org/cgit/linux/kernel/git/torvalds/linux.git/commit/?id=62421645bb702c077ee5a462815525106cb53bcf|title=Squashfs: Add LZ4 compression configuration option|accessdate=2015-08-28|author=Phillip Lougher|date=2014-11-27}}</ref>Yann Collet也在较新版的[[Zstd|Zstd]]压缩软件中实现了LZ4。

